  \_______| e l e s t e P a d

[ Made at Hack Club ]

CelestePad is a macropad made as a controller for
playing Celeste with keyboard controls.

There are two CelestePad versions planned:
  * CelestePad Origin: A low-cost keyboard for stationary use
  * CelestePad: A wired, split controller with magnetic accessories
